tickets.title: Bugs
tickets.description: You need to fix this Bug Asap

tickets.title: Broken login button
tickets.description: High priority: Login button not responding on mobile view.

tickets.title: Database connection timeout
tickets.description: High priority: Frequent timeout errors during ticket submission.

tickets.title: UI misalignment on dashboard
tickets.description: Low priority: Analytics cards overlap on smaller screens.

tickets.title: Email notification failure
tickets.description: Medium priority: Users not receiving password reset emails.

tickets.title: Slow dashboard loading time
tickets.description: Medium priority: Dashboard takes more than 10 seconds to load.

tickets.title: Ticket filtering not working
tickets.description: High priority: Users cannot filter tickets by status.

tickets.title: Forgot password link expired
tickets.description: Medium priority: Reset links expire in less than 1 minute.

tickets.title: Attachment upload error
tickets.description: High priority: Users cannot upload screenshots to tickets.

tickets.title: Duplicate ticket creation
tickets.description: High priority: System allows identical tickets for same user.

tickets.title: Search function returns wrong results
tickets.description: Medium priority: Searching by ID shows unrelated tickets.

tickets.title: Session timeout after login
tickets.description: High priority: Users logged out after 2 minutes of inactivity.
